            <thetext>If group-item is sticky and has a top border-radius  set, it might happen that list-items appear behind the rounded corners. For this purpose I added a special CSS rule which prevent that case:

877483b97ac6ea1e53584b1399090b13144423df

It contains a rectangle behind the first group-item in the color of the NavigationPage. If a list-items moves behind the rounded corner, it is not visible anymore.</thetext>
